{"tid":909803,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］主機前置面板咪問題","createTime":"2018-11-20T16:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T16:28:15.000Z","uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21fdf4bb2d0a78d45c0daec37df8d526a928e483","tid":909803,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"我新砌左部機，主機前置面板個2個孔，<br />\n一個係音樂，一個係咪，<br />\n但係我一插咪就有長響嗶嗶聲，<br />\n插音樂嗰邊就冇事，聽得好清楚。<br />\n<br />\n由於我係窮撚一個，<br />\n所以用apple耳機加條adapter<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wjGTR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wjGTR1.png&h=720ee9ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我試過插主機後面，<br />\n係function到，不論聲定係咪，<br />\n但一插前面就奶野。<br />\n但係就會唔夠長。<br />\n各位巴打幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bbc60be96461497b799e0794c4a19f1fb72e49","tid":909803,"uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf7c02aa96af0005620fa2d6450ec380b8b79600","tid":909803,"uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff11b1c4aa482db2ea57f3113508c323e1d5b9f8","tid":909803,"uid":21394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}